result.title: The Girl with Dimples
result.description: This story will walk you through a beautiful but brief encounter. Love need not be ages old to be felt, you can fall in love at the most unexpected time and similarly, you can also not fall in love even when met with beautiful feelings of love, but there is almost always an incomplete feeling, an incomplete expression that is left behind... the story beautifully expresses the same. Read through for more.
result.name: Abhisar Garg
